            </tr>
            <tr>
               <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left">865</td>
               <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left">42$81.3$a1969-1978$oTen year cumulative index</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
               <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>868</strong></td>
               <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>40</strong><strong>$8</strong>0<strong>$a</strong>1937-1942, 1946-1968, plus 1969/1978 cumulative
                                    vol.<br><em>[The 868 field provides an alternative display and replaces the 865 fields.]
